<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Mama, calmese, calmese.</i></font>

184
00:10:46,681 --> 00:10:48,447
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Papa</i> is coming home?</font>

185
00:10:48,448 --> 00:10:51,565
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, <i>Mama.</i>
