00:25:37,903 --> 00:25:39,970
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Mija,</i> it's not nice to stare at...</font>

371
00:25:39,971 --> 00:25:41,640
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Ay!</i> Santa Maria!</font>

372
00:25:49,316 --> 00:25:53,718
<font color="#FFFFFF">Are those...
Alebrijes! But those are...</font>

373
00:25:53,720 --> 00:25:56,253
<font color="#FFFFFF">Real alebrijes.
Spirit creatures.</font>

374
00:25:56,256 --> 00:25:58,122
<font color="#FFFFFF">They guide souls
on their journey.</font>

375
00:25:58,124 --> 00:26:00,592
<font color="#FFFFFF">Watch your step. They
make <i>caquitas</i> everywhere.</font>

376
00:26:00,594 --> 00:26:02,794
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Welcome back
to the Land of the Dead.</i></font>

377
00:26:02,796 --> 00:26:05,630
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Please have all offerings
ready for re-entry.</i></font>

378
00:26:05,632 --> 00:26:07,865
<font color="#FFFFFF">Welcome back.
Anything to declare?</font>

379
00:26:07,866 --> 00:26:09,333
<font color="#FFFFFF">Some churros.
From my family.</font>

380
00:26:09,335 --> 00:26:11,335
<font color="#FFFFFF">How wonderful. Next.</font>

381
00:26:11,336 --> 00:26:13,203
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>If you are
experiencing travel issues,</i></font>

382
00:26:13,207 --> 00:26:14,940
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>agents at
the Department of Family...</i></font>

383
00:26:14,942 --> 00:26:17,174
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Reunions are
available to assist you.</i></font>

384
00:26:17,176 --> 00:26:18,959
<font color="#FFFFFF">Next family, please.</font>

385
00:26:22,449 --> 00:26:25,016
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh! Your photos
are on your son's <i>ofrenda.</i></font>

386
00:26:25,018 --> 00:26:26,383
<font color="#FFFFFF">Have a great visit.</font>

387
00:26:26,384 --> 00:26:27,651
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Gracias.</i></font>

388
00:26:27,653 --> 00:26:29,688
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>And remember
to return before sunrise.</i></font>

389
00:26:29,690 --> 00:26:30,888
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Enjoy your visit.</i></font>

390
00:26:30,891 --> 00:26:33,223
<font color="#FFFFFF">Next.</font>

391
00:26:33,227 --> 00:26:36,759
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your photo's on your dentist's <i>ofrenda.</i>
Enjoy your visit.</font>

392
00:26:36,761 --> 00:26:38,544
<font color="#FFFFFF">- <i>Gracias.</i>
- Next?</font>

393
00:26:40,834 --> 00:26:43,067
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes! It is I.
Frida Kahlo.</font>

394
00:26:43,068 --> 00:26:44,634
<font color="#FFFFFF">Shall we skip
the scanner?</font>

395
00:26:44,636 --> 00:26:48,354
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm on so many <i>ofrendas</i> it'll just
overwhelm your blinky thingy.</font>

396
00:26:50,076 --> 00:26:54,645
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, shoot, looks like no one
put up your photo, Frida.</font>

397
00:26:54,647 --> 00:26:58,916
<font color="#FFFFFF">Okay, when I said I was Frida,
just now, that was a lie.</font>

398
00:26:58,919 --> 00:27:00,317
<font color="#FFFFFF">And I apologize
for doing that.</font>

399
00:27:00,318 --> 00:27:03,188
<font color="#FFFFFF">No photo on an <i>ofrenda,</i>
no crossing the bridge.</font>

400
00:27:03,190 --> 00:27:06,972
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm just gonna zip right over.
You won't even know I'm gone.</font>

401
00:27:07,928 --> 00:27:10,108
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey!</font>

402
00:27:15,669 --> 00:27:19,403
<font color="#FFFFFF">Almost... there.
Just a little further.</font>

403
00:27:24,211 --> 00:27:25,275
<font color="#FFFFFF">Upsy-daisy...</font>

404
00:27:25,278 --> 00:27:29,680
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fine. Okay. Fine, who cares?
Dumb flower bridge!</font>

405
00:27:29,682 --> 00:27:33,785
<font color="#FFFFFF">Aw. I don't know what I'd do
if no one put up my photo.</font>

406
00:27:33,787 --> 00:27:36,086
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Next?
- Oh! Come, <i>mijo.</i> It's our turn.</font>

407
00:27:36,087 --> 00:27:39,023
<font color="#FFFFFF">Welcome back, <i>amigos.</i>
Anything to declare?</font>

408
00:27:39,026 --> 00:27:42,442
<font color="#FFFFFF">As a matter of fact, yes.</font>

409
00:27:42,827 --> 00:27:44,143
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Hola.</i></font>

410
00:27:50,970 --> 00:27:53,137
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Paging Marta Gonzales-Ramos.</i></font>

411
00:27:53,140 --> 00:27:56,021
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Please report to Level Seven.</i></font>

412
00:28:00,314 --> 00:28:02,060
<font color="#FFFFFF">Whoa!</font>

413
00:28:05,250 --> 00:28:07,299
<font color="#FFFFFF">I miss my nose.</font>

414
00:28:16,328 --> 00:28:18,295
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on, help us out, <i>amigo.</i></font>

415
00:28:18,297 --> 00:28:19,763
<font color="#FFFFFF">We got to get to
a dozen <i>ofrendas</i> tonight.</font>

416
00:28:19,766 --> 00:28:23,901
<font color="#FFFFFF">We are not visiting your ex-wife's
family for <i>Dia de Muertos!</i></font>

417
00:28:23,903 --> 00:28:26,438
<font color="#FFFFFF">I demand to speak
to the person in charge!</font>

418
00:28:26,440 --> 00:28:29,340
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm sorry, <i>senora,</i> it says
here no one put up your photo.</font>

419
00:28:29,343 --> 00:28:33,911
<font color="#FFFFFF">My family always puts my
photo on the <i>ofrenda.</i></font>

420
00:28:33,913 --> 00:28:37,013
<font color="#FFFFFF">That devil box tells
you nothing but lies!</font>

421
00:28:37,016 --> 00:28:41,785
<font color="#FFFFFF">- <i>Mama</i> Imelda?
- Oh, <i>mi familia!</i></font>

422
00:28:41,787 --> 00:28:43,386
<font color="#FFFFFF">They wouldn't let me
cross the bridge.</font>

423
00:28:43,388 --> 00:28:45,890
<font color="#FFFFFF">Tell this woman
and her devil box</font>

424
00:28:45,893 --> 00:28:48,425
<font color="#FFFFFF">that my photo
is on the <i>ofrenda.</i></font>

425
00:28:48,427 --> 00:28:51,895
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, we never
made it to the <i>ofrenda.</i></font>

426
00:28:51,898 --> 00:28:55,615
<font color="#FFFFFF">- What?
- We ran into...</font>

427
00:28:58,304 --> 00:29:01,422
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Miguel?
<i>- Mama</i> Imelda.</font>

428
00:29:01,842 --> 00:29:04,174
<font color="#FFFFFF">What is going on?</font>

429
00:29:04,176 --> 00:29:06,478
<font color="#FFFFFF">You the Rivera family?</font>

430
00:29:08,080 --> 00:29:09,446
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, you're cursed.</font>

431
00:29:09,449 --> 00:29:10,582
<font color="#FFFFFF">What?</font>

432
00:29:10,584 --> 00:29:13,218
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Dia de los Muertos</i> is the
night to give to the dead.</font>

433
00:29:13,220 --> 00:29:14,818
<font color="#FFFFFF">You stole from the dead!</font>

434
00:29:14,820 --> 00:29:16,186
<font color="#FFFFFF">But I wasn't
stealing the guitar.</font>

435
00:29:16,190 --> 00:29:17,320
<font color="#FFFFFF">Guitar?</font>

436
00:29:17,323 --> 00:29:18,922
<font color="#FFFFFF">It was my
great-great-grandfather's.</font>

437
00:29:18,924 --> 00:29:20,224
<font color="#FFFFFF">He would have
wanted me to have it.</font>

438
00:29:20,227 --> 00:29:23,361
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ah, ah, ah. We do not speak
of that musician.</font>

439
00:29:23,363 --> 00:29:25,095
<font color="#FFFFFF">He is dead to this family.</font>

440
00:29:25,096 --> 00:29:27,064
<font color="#FFFFFF">Uh,
you're all dead.</font>

441
00:29:28,134 --> 00:29:30,801
<font color="#FFFFFF">I am sorry.
Whose alebrije is that?</font>

442
00:29:30,804 --> 00:29:32,068
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's just Dante.</font>

443
00:29:32,070 --> 00:29:34,204
<font color="#FFFFFF">He sure doesn't
look like an alebrije.</font>

444
00:29:34,208 --> 00:29:35,806
<font color="#FFFFFF">He just looks
like a plain old dog.</font>

445
00:29:35,807 --> 00:29:38,074
<font color="#FFFFFF">Or a sausage someone dropped
in a barbershop.</font>

446
00:29:38,076 --> 00:29:41,845
<font color="#FFFFFF">Whatever he is, I am
terribly allergic.</font>

447
00:29:41,846 --> 00:29:43,515
<font color="#FFFFFF">But Dante
doesn't have any hair.</font>

448
00:29:43,517 --> 00:29:46,217
<font color="#FFFFFF">And I don't have a nose,
and yet, here we are.</font>

449
00:29:47,421 --> 00:29:51,121
<font color="#FFFFFF">But none of this explains
why I couldn't cross over.</font>

450
00:29:51,123 --> 00:29:52,805
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh!</font>

451
00:29:54,259 --> 00:29:56,993
<font color="#FFFFFF">You took my photo
off the <i>ofrenda?</i></font>

452
00:29:56,996 --> 00:29:59,095
<font color="#FFFFFF">- It was an accident!
- How do we send him back?</font>

453
00:29:59,096 --> 00:30:01,833
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well,
since it's a family matter...</font>

454
00:30:01,835 --> 00:30:04,268
<font color="#FFFFFF">the way to undo
a family curse</font>

455
00:30:04,269 --> 00:30:07,003
<font color="#FFFFFF">- is to get your family's blessing.
- That's it?</font>

456
00:30:07,006 --> 00:30:08,405
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get your family's blessing</font>

457
00:30:08,407 --> 00:30:11,007
<font color="#FFFFFF">and everything should
go back to normal.</font>

458
00:30:11,009 --> 00:30:13,044
<font color="#FFFFFF">But you got
to do it by sunrise.</font>

459
00:30:13,046 --> 00:30:14,978
<font color="#FFFFFF">What happens at sunrise?</font>

460
00:30:14,980 --> 00:30:16,829
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Hijole!</i> Your hand!</font>

461
00:30:21,989 --> 00:30:24,855
<font color="#FFFFFF">Whoa, Miguel, can't have
you fainting on us.</font>

462
00:30:24,856 --> 00:30:27,424
<font color="#FFFFFF">But not to worry.
Your family's here.</font>

463
00:30:27,426 --> 00:30:29,460
<font color="#FFFFFF">You can get
your blessing right now.</font>

464
00:30:29,461 --> 00:30:34,431
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Cempasuchil, cempasuchil.</i>
Aha! <i>Perdon, senora.</i></font>

465
00:30:34,432 --> 00:30:35,400
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh.</font>

466
00:30:35,402 --> 00:30:38,318
<font color="#FFFFFF">Now, you look at the living
and say his name.</font>

467
00:30:39,204 --> 00:30:40,237
<font color="#FFFFFF">Miguel.</font>

468
00:30:40,239 --> 00:30:43,540
<font color="#FFFFFF">Nailed it. Now say,
"I give you my blessing."</font>

469
00:30:43,544 --> 00:30:45,592
<font color="#FFFFFF">I give you my blessing.</font>

470
00:30:48,015 --> 00:30:51,413
<font color="#FFFFFF">I give you my blessing
to go home...</font>

471
00:30:51,415 --> 00:30:54,585
<font color="#FFFFFF">to put my photo
back on the <i>ofrenda,</i></font>

472
00:30:54,586 --> 00:30:57,021
<font color="#FFFFFF">and to never
play music again.</font>

473
00:30:57,023 --> 00:30:58,890
<font color="#FFFFFF">What? She can't do that!</font>

474
00:30:58,892 --> 00:31:02,159
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, technically, she can
add any condition she wants.</font>

475
00:31:02,161 --> 00:31:04,294
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fine.</font>

476
00:31:04,297 --> 00:31:06,512
<font color="#FFFFFF">Then you hand
the petal to Miguel.</font>

477
00:31:19,046 --> 00:31:20,393
<font color="#FFFFFF">No skeletons!</font>

478
00:31:24,482 --> 00:31:26,765
<font color="#FFFFFF">Mariachi Plaza,
here I come.</font>

479
00:31:30,990 --> 00:31:33,189
<font color="#FFFFFF">Two seconds and you already
break your promise.</font>

480
00:31:33,191 --> 00:31:37,061
<font color="#FFFFFF">This isn't fair. It's my life.
You already had yours.</font>

481
00:31:37,064 --> 00:31:39,130
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Papa</i> Julio,
I ask for your blessing.</font>

482
00:31:39,132 --> 00:31:42,232
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Tia</i> Rosita? Oscar?</font>

483
00:31:42,236 --> 00:31:45,102
<font color="#FFFFFF">Felipe? <i>Tia</i> Victoria?</font>

484
00:31:45,104 --> 00:31:49,506
<font color="#FFFFFF">Don't make this hard, <i>mijo.</i>
You go home my way or no way.</font>

485
00:31:49,508 --> 00:31:51,374
<font color="#FFFFFF">You really hate
music that much?</font>

486
00:31:51,375 --> 00:31:54,526
<font color="#FFFFFF">I will not let you go down
the same path he did.</font>

487
00:31:56,950 --> 00:32:01,151
<font color="#FFFFFF">The same path he did.
He's family.</font>

488
00:32:01,153 --> 00:32:02,953
<font color="#FFFFFF">Listen to your <i>Mama</i> Imelda.</font>

489
00:32:02,955 --> 00:32:04,220
<font color="#FFFFFF">She's just
looking out for you.</font>

490
00:32:04,221 --> 00:32:05,288
<font color="#FFFFFF">Be reasonable.</font>

491
00:32:05,290 --> 00:32:08,625
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Con permiso,</i>
I need to visit the restroom.</font>

492
00:32:08,627 --> 00:32:10,410
<font color="#FFFFFF">Be right back.</font>

493
00:32:11,265 --> 00:32:13,364
<font color="#FFFFFF">Uh, should we tell him
there are no restrooms</font>

494
00:32:13,365 --> 00:32:14,680
<font color="#FFFFFF">in the Land of the Dead?</font>

495
00:32:27,712 --> 00:32:28,880
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Vamonos.</i></font>

496
00:32:28,882 --> 00:32:31,583
<font color="#FFFFFF">We got a family
looking for a living boy.</font>

497
00:32:31,585 --> 00:32:34,317
<font color="#FFFFFF">If I want to be a musician,
I need a musician's blessing.</font>

498
00:32:34,319 --> 00:32:36,387
<font color="#FFFFFF">We got to find
my great-great-grandpa.</font>

499
00:32:36,390 --> 00:32:38,439
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hold it, <i>muchacho.</i></font>

500
00:32:42,028 --> 00:32:43,394
<font color="#FFFFFF">I found that living boy!</font>

501
00:32:43,395 --> 00:32:45,628
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, whoa, excuse me.
Excuse me, folks.</font>

502
00:32:45,631 --> 00:32:46,980
<font color="#FFFFFF">Excuse me.</font>

503
00:32:47,732 --> 00:32:49,248
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh.</font>

504
00:32:53,006 --> 00:32:55,271
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, no. Dante!</font>

505
00:32:55,273 --> 00:32:58,307
<font color="#FFFFFF">Disturbing the peace.
Fleeing an officer.</font>

506
00:32:58,310 --> 00:33:00,176
<font color="#FFFFFF">Falsifying a unibrow.</font>

507
00:33:00,179 --> 00:33:02,445
<font color="#FFFFFF">- That's illegal?
- Very illegal.</font>

508
00:33:02,448 --> 00:33:04,547
<font color="#FFFFFF">You need to clean up
your act, <i>amigo.</i></font>

509
00:33:04,548 --> 00:33:08,285
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Amigo?</i> Oh, that's so nice
to hear you say that</font>

510
00:33:08,287 --> 00:33:10,086
<font color="#FFFFFF">because I have just had a...</font>

511
00:33:10,087 --> 00:33:13,023
<font color="#FFFFFF">really hard <i>Dia de Muertos</i>
and I could really use</font>

512
00:33:13,026 --> 00:33:14,025
<font color="#FFFFFF">an <i>amigo</i> right now.</font>

513
00:33:14,027 --> 00:33:16,759
<font color="#FFFFFF">And <i>amigos,</i>
they help their <i>amigos.</i></font>

514
00:33:16,761 --> 00:33:19,461
<font color="#FFFFFF">You get me across
that bridge tonight,</font>

515
00:33:19,463 --> 00:33:21,065
<font color="#FFFFFF">and I'll make it
worth your while.</font>

516
00:33:21,067 --> 00:33:24,169
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh! You like de la Cruz?
He and I go way back.</font>

517
00:33:24,171 --> 00:33:27,505
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can get you front row seats to
his Sunrise Spectacular show.</font>

518
00:33:27,507 --> 00:33:29,708
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll get you backstage.
You can meet him.</font>

519
00:33:29,710 --> 00:33:31,442
<font color="#FFFFFF">You just got to let me
cross that bridge!</font>

520
00:33:31,443 --> 00:33:33,612
<font color="#FFFFFF">I should lock you up
for the rest of the holiday.</font>

521
00:33:33,614 --> 00:33:37,715
<font color="#FFFFFF">But my shift's almost up and I
want to visit my living family.</font>

522
00:33:37,718 --> 00:33:40,432
<font color="#FFFFFF">So I'm letting you off
with a warning.</font>

523
00:33:41,385 --> 00:33:43,520
<font color="#FFFFFF">Can I at least
get my costume back?</font>

524
00:33:43,523 --> 00:33:45,322
<font color="#FFFFFF">Uh... No.</font>

525
00:33:45,324 --> 00:33:47,807
<font color="#FFFFFF">Some <i>amigo.</i></font>

526
00:33:50,262 --> 00:33:53,730
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey! Hey!
You really know de la Cruz?</font>

527
00:33:53,732 --> 00:33:56,366
<font color="#FFFFFF">Who wants to... Ahh!
<i>Ay!</i> You're alive!</font>

528
00:33:56,368 --> 00:33:58,068
<font color="#FFFFFF">Shh! Yeah, I'm alive.</font>

529
00:33:58,070 --> 00:34:00,136
<font color="#FFFFFF">And if I want to get back
to the Land of the Living...</font>

530
00:34:00,138 --> 00:34:01,604
<font color="#FFFFFF">I need de la Cruz's blessing.</font>

531
00:34:01,605 --> 00:34:03,208
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's weirdly specific.</font>

532
00:34:03,210 --> 00:34:04,741
<font color="#FFFFFF">He's my
great-great-grandfather.</font>

533
00:34:04,743 --> 00:34:07,326
<font color="#FFFFFF">He's your Gr... What?</font>

534
00:34:07,748 --> 00:34:09,679
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ugh.</font>

535
00:34:09,681 --> 00:34:13,534
<font color="#FFFFFF">Wait, wait, wait.
Wait, wait.</font>

536
00:34:14,387 --> 00:34:16,487
<font color="#FFFFFF">Wait. No, wait, wait, wait.</font>

537
00:34:16,489 --> 00:34:20,623
<font color="#FFFFFF">Wait! Yes! You're going back
to the Land of the Living!</font>

538
00:34:20,625 --> 00:34:22,625
<font color="#FFFFFF">You know what? Maybe this
isn't such a good...</font>

539
00:34:22,626 --> 00:34:25,360
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, no, <i>nino! Nino, nino,</i> I can help you.
You can help me.</font>

540
00:34:25,362 --> 00:34:26,496
<font color="#FFFFFF">We can help each other.</font>

541
00:34:26,498 --> 00:34:28,364
<font color="#FFFFFF">But most importantly,
you can help me.</font>

542
00:34:28,365 --> 00:34:29,867
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Miguel!
- I'm Hector.</font>

543
00:34:29,869 --> 00:34:31,416
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's nice.</font>

544
00:34:36,108 --> 00:34:37,757
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Esperame, chamaco!</i></font>

545
00:34:45,585 --> 00:34:48,152
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Ay,</i> he is going
to get himself killed.</font>

546
00:34:48,155 --> 00:34:51,771
<font color="#FFFFFF">I need my spirit guide...
Pepita.</font>

547
00:35:03,467 --> 00:35:05,536
<font color="#FFFFFF">Who has that petal
Miguel touched?</font>

548
00:35:05,539 --> 00:35:08,653
<font color="#FFFFFF">Here. Nice alebrije.</font>

549
00:35:21,686 --> 00:35:26,003
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Ay, ay,</i> hold still. Look up. <i>A ver, a ver.</i>
Look up, up, up.</font>

550
00:35:27,293 --> 00:35:32,427
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Aqui arriba, eso...</i>
Eh, <i>la rayita.</i></font>

551
00:35:32,429 --> 00:35:35,012
<font color="#FFFFFF">Okay. Hey! Ta-da!</font>

552
00:35:35,701 --> 00:35:37,550
<font color="#FFFFFF">Dead as a doorknob.</font>

553
00:35:38,503 --> 00:35:41,605
<font color="#FFFFFF">So listen, Miguel,
this place runs on memories.</font>

554
00:35:41,606 --> 00:35:42,840
<font color="#FFFFFF">When you're well remembered,</font>

555
00:35:42,842 --> 00:35:44,706
<font color="#FFFFFF">people put up your photo
and you get to...</font>

556
00:35:44,708 --> 00:35:46,309
<font color="#FFFFFF">cross the bridge
and visit the living</font>

