- Um...</font>

588
00:36:57,382 --> 00:36:59,650
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, you said you have
front row tickets!</font>

589
00:36:59,652 --> 00:37:02,853
<font color="#FFFFFF">That... was a lie.
I apologize for that.</font>

590
00:37:02,855 --> 00:37:05,021
<font color="#FFFFFF">Cool off, <i>chamaco.</i>
Come on. I'll get you to him.</font>

591
00:37:05,023 --> 00:37:06,123
<font color="#FFFFFF">How?</font>

592
00:37:06,125 --> 00:37:08,240
<font color="#FFFFFF">Because I happen to know
where he's rehearsing.</font>

593
00:37:18,802 --> 00:37:22,987
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ Remember me
Don't let it make you cry ♪</i></font>

594
00:37:24,277 --> 00:37:26,541
<font color="#FFFFFF">You better have
my dress, Hector.</font>

595
00:37:26,543 --> 00:37:27,925
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Hola,</i> Ceci.</font>

596
00:37:33,753 --> 00:37:38,023
<font color="#FFFFFF">- <i>Hola.</i>
- Ceci, I lost the dress.</font>

597
00:37:38,025 --> 00:37:39,690
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Ya lo sabia!</i></font>

598
00:37:39,692 --> 00:37:41,958
<font color="#FFFFFF">I got to dress
