601
00:38:04,849 --> 00:38:07,166
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, no, Dante! <i>Ven aca!</i></font>

602
00:38:15,994 --> 00:38:17,860
<font color="#FFFFFF">You! How did you
get in here?</font>

603
00:38:17,862 --> 00:38:22,030
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I just followed my...
- Oh! The mighty Xolo dog!</font>

604
00:38:22,032 --> 00:38:25,001
<font color="#FFFFFF">Guider of wandering spirits.</font>

605
00:38:25,003 --> 00:38:28,038
<font color="#FFFFFF">And whose spirit
have you guided to me?</font>

606
00:38:28,039 --> 00:38:30,405
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't think
he's a spirit guide.</font>

607
00:38:30,407 --> 00:38:31,407
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ah, ah, ah.</font>

608
00:38:31,409 --> 00:38:34,478
<font color="#FFFFFF">The alebrijes of this world
can take many forms.</font>

609
00:38:34,480 --> 00:38:37,797
<font color="#FFFFFF">They are as mysterious
as they are powerful.</font>

610
00:38:43,387 --> 00:38:47,239
<font color="#FFFFFF">Or maybe he's just a dog.
Come, I need your eyes.</font>

611
00:38:48,492 --> 00:38:52,663
<font color="#FFFFFF">You are the audience.
Darkness.</font>

612
00:38:52,664 --> 00:38:56,882
<font color="#FFFFFF">And from the darkness,
a giant papaya.</font>

613
00:38:57,838 --> 00:39:00,838
<font color="#FFFFFF">Dancers emerge
from the papaya,</font>

614
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:04,907
<font color="#FFFFFF">and the dancers are all me.</font>

615
00:39:04,911 --> 00:39:07,643
<font color="#FFFFFF">And they go to drink from
the milk of their mother,</font>

616
00:39:07,646 --> 00:39:08,847
<font color="#FFFFFF">who is a cactus.</font>

617
00:39:08,849 --> 00:39:10,581
<font color="#FFFFFF">But who is also me.</font>

618
00:39:10,583 --> 00:39:14,900
<font color="#FFFFFF">And her milk is
not milk but tears.</font>

619
00:39:15,856 --> 00:39:16,920
<font color="#FFFFFF">Is it too obvious?</font>

620
00:39:16,922 --> 00:39:20,655
<font color="#FFFFFF">I think it's just
the right amount of obvious?</font>

621
00:39:20,659 --> 00:39:24,059
<font color="#FFFFFF">It could use some music.
Oh, what if you did like...</font>

622
00:39:27,465 --> 00:39:28,931
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh! And then it could go...</font>

623
00:39:34,539 --> 00:39:37,409
<font color="#FFFFFF">And what if
