624
00:39:37,411 --> 00:39:39,610
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes! Fire! Everywhere!</font>

625
00:39:39,612 --> 00:39:43,813
<font color="#FFFFFF">Inspired! You have
the spirit of an artist.</font>

626
00:39:45,750 --> 00:39:48,686
<font color="#FFFFFF">The dancers exit. The music
fades, the lights go out.</font>

627
00:39:48,688 --> 00:39:52,021
<font color="#FFFFFF">And Ernesto de la Cruz
rises to the stage!</font>

628
00:39:55,827 --> 00:39:57,126
<font color="#FFFFFF">Huh?</font>

629
00:39:57,128 --> 00:39:59,461
<font color="#FFFFFF">He does a couple of songs, the
sun rises, everyone cheers...</font>

630
00:39:59,463 --> 00:40:01,998
<font color="#FFFFFF">Excuse me,
where's the real de la Cruz?</font>

631
00:40:02,000 --> 00:40:04,099
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ernesto doesn't do
rehearsals!</font>

632
00:40:04,101 --> 00:40:08,018
<font color="#FFFFFF">He's too busy hosting that fancy
party at the top of his tower.</font>

633
00:40:11,344 --> 00:40:13,643
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Chamaco,</i> you can't run off
on me like that.</font>

634
00:40:13,646 --> 00:40:15,478
<font color="#FFFFFF">Stop pestering
the celebrities.</font>

635
00:40:15,480 --> 00:40:17,648
<font color="#FFFFFF">You said my great-great-grandpa
would be here!</font>

636
00:40:17,650 --> 00:40:20,516
<font color="#FFFFFF">He's halfway across town
throwing some big party.</font>

637
00:40:20,518 --> 00:40:22,920
<font color="#FFFFFF">That bum. Who doesn't show up
to his own rehearsal?</font>

638
00:40:22,922 --> 00:40:25,855
<font color="#FFFFFF">If you're such good friends,
how come he didn't invite you?</font>

639
00:40:25,856 --> 00:40:28,726
<font color="#FFFFFF">He's your great-great-grandpa,
how come he didn't invite you?</font>

640
00:40:28,728 --> 00:40:31,728
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, Gustavo! You know
anything about this party?</font>

641
00:40:31,731 --> 00:40:33,163
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's the hot ticket!</font>

642
00:40:33,164 --> 00:40:34,764
<font color="#FFFFFF">But if you're not
on the guest list,</font>

643
00:40:34,766 --> 00:40:37,202
<font color="#FFFFFF">you're never
getting in, <i>Chorizo.</i></font>

644
00:40:37,204 --> 00:40:40,001
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey! It's <i>Chorizo! Choricito!</i></font>

645
00:40:40,005 --> 00:40:41,637
<font color="#FFFFFF">A-ha. Very funny, guys.
Very funny.</font>

646
00:40:41,641 --> 00:40:42,873
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Chorizo?</i></font>

647
00:40:42,875 --> 00:40:45,007
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, this guy's famous!</font>

648
00:40:45,010 --> 00:40:47,143
<font color="#FFFFFF">Go on, go on.
Ask him how he died.</font>

649
00:40:47,144 --> 00:40:48,778
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't want
to talk about it.</font>

650
00:40:48,780 --> 00:40:51,914
<font color="#FFFFFF">He choked on some <i>chorizo!</i></font>

651
00:40:54,018 --> 00:40:55,753
<font color="#FFFFFF">I didn't choke, okay?</font>

652
00:40:55,755 --> 00:40:57,755
<font color="#FFFFFF">I got food poisoning
which is a big difference.</font>

653
00:40:58,889 --> 00:41:00,523
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is why
I don't like musicians.</font>

654
00:41:00,525 --> 00:41:02,157
<font color="#FFFFFF">Bunch of
self-important jerks.</font>

655
00:41:02,159 --> 00:41:04,661
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Hey! I'm a musician!
- You are?</font>

656
00:41:04,664 --> 00:41:07,498
<font color="#FFFFFF">If you really want
to get to Ernesto,</font>

657
00:41:07,501 --> 00:41:08,898
<font color="#FFFFFF">there is that
music competition...</font>

658
00:41:08,900 --> 00:41:10,567
<font color="#FFFFFF">at the Plaza de la Cruz.</font>

659
00:41:10,570 --> 00:41:13,119
<font color="#FFFFFF">Winner gets
to play at his party.</font>

660
00:41:14,072 --> 00:41:17,074
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, no. <i>Chamaco,</i>
you're <i>loco</i> if you think...</font>

661
00:41:17,076 --> 00:41:19,510
<font color="#FFFFFF">I need to get my
great-great-grandfather's blessing!</font>

662
00:41:19,512 --> 00:41:21,393
<font color="#FFFFFF">You know where
