663
00:41:21,981 --> 00:41:25,262
<font color="#FFFFFF">I know a guy.</font>

664
00:41:36,795 --> 00:41:39,929
<font color="#FFFFFF">Have you found him, Pepita?
Have you found our boy?</font>

665
00:41:41,132 --> 00:41:43,932
<font color="#FFFFFF">- A footprint!
- It's a Rivera boot.</font>

666
00:41:43,934 --> 00:41:45,802
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Size seven!
- And a half.</font>

667
00:41:45,804 --> 00:41:48,253
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Pronated.
- Miguel.</font>

668
00:41:57,750 --> 00:41:59,682
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why the heck would
you want to be a musician?</font>

669
00:41:59,684 --> 00:42:01,552
<font color="#FFFFFF">My great-great-grandpa
was a musician!</font>

670
00:42:01,554 --> 00:42:03,085
<font color="#FFFFFF">Who spent his life
performing like a monkey</font>

671
00:42:03,088 --> 00:42:04,887
<font color="#FFFFFF">for complete strangers.</font>

672
00:42:04,889 --> 00:42:07,291
<font color="#FFFFFF">No thank you.
No! <i>Guacala!</i></font>

673
00:42:07,293 --> 00:42:09,157
<font color="#FFFFFF">What do you know?</font>

674
00:42:09,159 --> 00:42:11,563
<font color="#FFFFFF">So, how far is
this guitar anyway?</font>

675
00:42:11,565 --> 00:42:12,945
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're almost there.</font>

676
00:42:17,769 --> 00:42:19,351
<font color="#FFFFFF">Keep up, <i>chamaco.</i> Come on.</font>

677
00:42:28,014 --> 00:42:32,715
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Cousin Hector!
