680
00:42:35,320 --> 00:42:36,686
<font color="#FFFFFF">Uh...</font>

681
00:42:36,688 --> 00:42:40,023
<font color="#FFFFFF">In a way. We're all the ones
with no photos or <i>ofrendas.</i></font>

682
00:42:40,025 --> 00:42:43,159
<font color="#FFFFFF">No family to go home to.
