683
00:42:43,161 --> 00:42:47,313
<font color="#FFFFFF">So, we all call each other
cousin, or <i>tio,</i> or whatever.</font>

684
00:42:51,735 --> 00:42:54,251
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Hector!
- <i>Tia</i> Chelo!</font>

685
00:42:56,041 --> 00:42:58,141
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Muchas gracias!</i></font>

686
00:42:58,143 --> 00:43:00,675
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey! Save some for me!
Is Chicharron around?</font>

687
00:43:00,679 --> 00:43:01,844
<font color="#FFFFFF">Eh, in the bungalow.</font>

688
00:43:01,846 --> 00:43:04,347
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't know if he's in
the mood for visitors.</font>

689
00:43:04,349 --> 00:43:07,632
<font color="#FFFFFF">Who doesn't like
a visit from Cousin Hector?</font>

690
00:43:16,795 --> 00:43:18,661
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Buenas noches,</i> Chicharron!</font>

691
00:43:18,663 --> 00:43:21,097
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't want to see
your stupid face, Hector.</font>

692
00:43:21,099 --> 00:43:23,166
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on.
It's <i>Dia de Muertos.</i></font>

693
00:43:23,168 --> 00:43:24,768
<font color="#FFFFFF">I brought you
a little offering.</font>

694
00:43:24,769 --> 00:43:26,836
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Get out of here.
- I would, Cheech.</font>

695
00:43:26,838 --> 00:43:29,487
<font color="#FFFFFF">But the thing is,
me and my friend, Miguel...</font>

696
00:43:30,643 --> 00:43:32,340
<font color="#FFFFFF">We really need
