697
00:43:32,344 --> 00:43:33,911
<font color="#FFFFFF">- My guitar?
- Yes.</font>

698
00:43:33,913 --> 00:43:36,211
<font color="#FFFFFF">My prized beloved guitar?</font>

699
00:43:36,213 --> 00:43:38,047
<font color="#FFFFFF">I promise
we'll bring it right back.</font>

700
00:43:38,048 --> 00:43:40,717
<font color="#FFFFFF">Like the time you promised
to bring back my van?</font>

701
00:43:40,719 --> 00:43:42,186
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Uh...
