703
00:43:43,922 --> 00:43:45,755
<font color="#FFFFFF">My lasso? My femur?</font>

704
00:43:45,757 --> 00:43:46,989
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well, no,
not like those times.</font>

705
00:43:46,992 --> 00:43:49,326
<font color="#FFFFFF">Where is my femur?
