706
00:43:49,327 --> 00:43:51,327
<font color="#FFFFFF">Whoa, whoa.</font>

707
00:43:51,329 --> 00:43:55,246
<font color="#FFFFFF">- You okay, <i>amigo?</i>
- I'm fading, Hector.</font>

708
00:43:55,835 --> 00:43:58,268
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can feel it.</font>

709
00:43:58,271 --> 00:44:01,452
<font color="#FFFFFF">I couldn't even play
that thing if I wanted to.</font>

710
00:44:04,675 --> 00:44:07,210
<font color="#FFFFFF">You play me something.</font>

711
00:44:07,213 --> 00:44:09,278
<font color="#FFFFFF">No. You know
I don't play anymore, Cheech.</font>

712
00:44:09,282 --> 00:44:11,215
<font color="#FFFFFF">The guitar is for the kid.</font>

713
00:44:11,217 --> 00:44:15,000
<font color="#FFFFFF">You want it,
you got to earn it.</font>

714
00:44:16,389 --> 00:44:19,271
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Ay,</i> only for you, <i>amigo.</i></font>

715
00:44:21,826 --> 00:44:23,226
<font color="#FFFFFF">Any requests?</font>

716
00:44:23,228 --> 00:44:27,311
<font color="#FFFFFF">You know my favorite, Hector.</font>

717
00:44:44,784 --> 00:44:48,500
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ Well,
everyone knows Juanita</i></font>

718
00:44:49,454 --> 00:44:53,072
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ Her eyes
each a different color</i></font>

719
00:44:54,759 --> 00:44:59,443
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ Her teeth stick out
And her chin goes in</i></font>

720
00:45:00,398 --> 00:45:03,047
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ And her...</i></font>

721
00:45:04,001 --> 00:45:07,135
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ Knuckles they
drag on the floor</i></font>

722
00:45:07,137 --> 00:45:09,771
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Those aren't the words.
- There are children present.</font>

723
00:45:09,773 --> 00:45:13,523
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ Her hair is like a briar</i></font>

724
00:45:14,480 --> 00:45:18,463
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ She stands in
a bow-legged stance</i></font>

725
00:45:20,150 --> 00:45:24,469
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ And if I weren't so ugly</i></font>

726
00:45:26,157 --> 00:45:31,677
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ She'd possibly
give me a chance ♪</i></font>

727
00:45:37,369 --> 00:45:40,083
<font color="#FFFFFF">Brings back memories.</font>

728
00:45:44,242 --> 00:45:46,224
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Gracias.</i></font>

729
00:46:17,143 --> 00:46:19,474
<font color="#FFFFFF">Wait. What happened?</font>

730
00:46:19,476 --> 00:46:21,512
<font color="#FFFFFF">He's been forgotten.</font>

731
00:46:21,514 --> 00:46:23,077
<font color="#FFFFFF">When there's no one left
in the living world</font>

732
00:46:23,079 --> 00:46:24,414
<font color="#FFFFFF">who remembers you...</font>

733
00:46:24,416 --> 00:46:27,215
<font color="#FFFFFF">you disappear
from this world.</font>

734
00:46:27,217 --> 00:46:30,152
<font color="#FFFFFF">We call it
the final death.</font>

735
00:46:30,155 --> 00:46:32,355
<font color="#FFFFFF">Where did he go?</font>

736
00:46:32,356 --> 00:46:33,623
<font color="#FFFFFF">No one knows.</font>

737
00:46:33,626 --> 00:46:37,827
<font color="#FFFFFF">But I've met him. I could
remember him when I go back!</font>

738
00:46:37,829 --> 00:46:40,164
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, it doesn't work
like that, <i>chamaco.</i></font>

739
00:46:40,166 --> 00:46:43,132
<font color="#FFFFFF">Our memories,
they have to be passed down</font>

740
00:46:43,134 --> 00:46:44,967
<font color="#FFFFFF">by those
who knew us in life...</font>

741
00:46:44,971 --> 00:46:48,838
