939
01:00:45,110 --> 01:00:46,807
<font color="#FFFFFF">Are you all right, <i>nino?</i></font>

940
01:00:50,813 --> 01:00:53,849
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's you!
You are that boy!</font>

941
01:00:53,851 --> 01:00:55,983
<font color="#FFFFFF">The one who came
from the Land of the Living.</font>

942
01:00:55,985 --> 01:00:58,086
<font color="#FFFFFF">You... know about me?</font>

943
01:00:58,088 --> 01:01:01,324
<font color="#FFFFFF">You are all anyone
has been talking about.</font>

944
01:01:01,326 --> 01:01:03,693
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why have you come here?</font>

945
01:01:03,695 --> 01:01:07,996
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm Miguel.
Your great-great-grandson.</font>

946
01:01:09,099 --> 01:01:11,465
<font color="#FFFFFF">I... have
a great-great-grandson?</font>

947
01:01:11,467 --> 01:01:13,367
<font color="#FFFFFF">I need your blessing</font>

948
01:01:13,369 --> 01:01:15,704
<font color="#FFFFFF">so I can go back home
and be a musician.</font>

949
01:01:15,706 --> 01:01:17,373
<font color="#FFFFFF">Just like you.</font>

950
01:01:17,375 --> 01:01:21,210
<font color="#FFFFFF">The rest of our family,
they wouldn't listen.</font>

951
01:01:21,211 --> 01:01:24,262
<font color="#FFFFFF">But I hoped you would.</font>

952
01:01:25,951 --> 01:01:30,701
<font color="#FFFFFF">My boy, with a talent like
yours, how could I not listen?</font>

953
01:01:31,954 --> 01:01:33,855
<font color="#FFFFFF">Aww!</font>

954
01:01:33,856 --> 01:01:36,257
<font color="#FFFFFF">I have a great-great-grandson!</font>

955
01:01:42,833 --> 01:01:46,268
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Look! It's Frida!
- Yes, it is I. Frida Kahlo.</font>

956
01:01:46,271 --> 01:01:49,286
<font color="#FFFFFF">- It is an honor, <i>Senora.</i>
<i>- Gracias.</i></font>

957
01:01:53,309 --> 01:01:55,277
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, Negrete! Infante!</font>

958
01:01:55,280 --> 01:01:57,512
<font color="#FFFFFF">Have you met
my great-great-grandson?</font>

959
01:01:57,514 --> 01:01:59,414
<font color="#FFFFFF">My great-great-grandson.</font>

960
01:01:59,416 --> 01:02:01,983
<font color="#FFFFFF">He's alive!
And a musician to boot!</font>

961
01:02:01,987 --> 01:02:04,018
<font color="#FFFFFF">Dimple. No dimple.
Dimple. No dimple.</font>

962
01:02:04,021 --> 01:02:05,119
<font color="#FFFFFF">No dimple!</font>

963
01:02:05,121 --> 01:02:06,556
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>To our friendship.</i></font>

964
01:02:06,559 --> 01:02:10,440
<font color="#FFFFFF">I would move Heaven and
Earth for you, <i>mi amigo. Salud!</i></font>

965
01:02:11,862 --> 01:02:13,427
<font color="#FFFFFF">Poison!</font>

966
01:02:13,429 --> 01:02:15,764
<font color="#FFFFFF">You know,
I did all my own stunts.</font>

967
01:02:15,766 --> 01:02:19,617
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>♪ Though I have to say
goodbye Remember me... ♪</i></font>

968
01:02:21,306 --> 01:02:24,005
<font color="#FFFFFF">All of this
came from my amazing fans</font>

969
01:02:24,009 --> 01:02:26,407
<font color="#FFFFFF">in the Land of the Living.</font>

970
01:02:26,409 --> 01:02:30,445
<font color="#FFFFFF">They leave me more offerings
than I know what to do with!</font>

971
01:02:30,447 --> 01:02:34,048
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, what's wrong? Is it too much?
You look overwhelmed.</font>

972
01:02:34,050 --> 01:02:37,320
<font color="#FFFFFF">- No! It's all great!
- But?</font>

973
01:02:37,322 --> 01:02:39,420
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's just...</font>

974
01:02:39,422 --> 01:02:41,824
<font color="#FFFFFF">I have been looking up to you
my whole life.</font>

975
01:02:41,826 --> 01:02:45,208
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're the guy
who actually did it!</font>

976
01:02:46,163 --> 01:02:49,097
<font color="#FFFFFF">But did you ever regret it?</font>

977
01:02:49,099 --> 01:02:52,516
<font color="#FFFFFF">Choosing music
over everything else?</font>

978
01:02:52,936 --> 01:02:54,469
<font color="#FFFFFF">It was hard.</font>

979
01:02:54,471 --> 01:02:58,521
<font color="#FFFFFF">Saying goodbye to my hometown.
Heading off on my own...</font>

980
01:02:59,476 --> 01:03:01,476
<font color="#FFFFFF">Leaving your family?</font>

981
01:03:01,478 --> 01:03:06,382
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Si.</i> But I could not have
done it differently.</font>

982
01:03:06,384 --> 01:03:09,985
<font color="#FFFFFF">One cannot deny
who one is meant to be.</font>

983
01:03:09,987 --> 01:03:14,403
<font color="#FFFFFF">And you, my great-great-grandson,
are meant to be a musician!</font>

984
01:03:16,827 --> 01:03:19,327
<font color="#FFFFFF">You and I,
we are artists, Miguel.</font>

985
01:03:19,331 --> 01:03:21,329
<font color="#FFFFFF">We cannot
belong to one family.</font>

986
01:03:21,333 --> 01:03:23,815
<font color="#FFFFFF">The world is our family.</font>

987
01:03:25,235 --> 01:03:28,251
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ooh! Ooh!
The fireworks have begun!</font>

988
01:03:38,514 --> 01:03:42,983
<font color="#FFFFFF">Soon the party will move across
town for my Sunrise Spectacular.</font>

989
01:03:42,987 --> 01:03:45,954
<font color="#FFFFFF">Miguel,
you must come to the show!</font>

990
01:03:45,956 --> 01:03:47,989
<font color="#FFFFFF">You will be
my guest of honor!</font>

991
01:03:47,992 --> 01:03:50,409
<font color="#FFFFFF">- You mean it?
- Of course, my boy.</font>

992
01:03:52,097 --> 01:03:54,262
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can't.</font>

993
01:03:54,264 --> 01:03:56,965
<font color="#FFFFFF">I have to get home
before sunrise.</font>

994
01:03:56,967 --> 01:03:59,282
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh! I really do
need to get you home.</font>

995
01:04:03,275 --> 01:04:06,139
<font color="#FFFFFF">It has been an honor.</font>

996
01:04:06,141 --> 01:04:08,543
<font color="#FFFFFF">I am sorry
to see you go, Miguel.</font>

997
01:04:08,545 --> 01:04:10,427
<font color="#FFFFFF">I hope you die very soon.</font>

998
01:04:12,048 --> 01:04:14,632
<font color="#FFFFFF">You know what I mean.</font>

999
01:04:16,655 --> 01:04:19,454
<font color="#FFFFFF">Miguel, I give you my bless...</font>

1000
01:04:19,456 --> 01:04:21,521
<font color="#FFFFFF">We had a deal, <i>chamaco.</i></font>

1001
01:04:21,523 --> 01:04:25,159
<font color="#FFFFFF">Who are you?
What is the meaning of this?</font>

1002
01:04:25,161 --> 01:04:27,996
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, Frida! I thought
you couldn't make it.</font>

1003
01:04:27,998 --> 01:04:30,164
<font color="#FFFFFF">You said
you'd take back my photo.</font>

1004
01:04:30,166 --> 01:04:31,567
<font color="#FFFFFF">You promised, Miguel.</font>

1005
01:04:31,568 --> 01:04:33,603
<font color="#FFFFFF">You know this, uh, man?</font>

1006
01:04:33,605 --> 01:04:37,355
<font color="#FFFFFF">Uh, I just met him tonight.
He told me he knew you.</font>

1007
01:04:37,574 --> 01:04:39,608
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hector?</font>

1008
01:04:39,610 --> 01:04:42,893
<font color="#FFFFFF">Please, Miguel.
Put my photo up.</font>

1009
01:04:44,914 --> 01:04:49,052
<font color="#FFFFFF">My friend,
you're being forgotten.</font>

1010
01:04:49,054 --> 01:04:50,684
<font color="#FFFFFF">- And whose fault is that?
- Hector, please...</font>

1011
01:04:50,688 --> 01:04:53,489
<font color="#FFFFFF">Those were my songs you took.
My songs that made you famous.</font>

1012
01:04:53,490 --> 01:04:54,556
<font color="#FFFFFF">What?</font>

1013
01:04:54,557 --> 01:04:56,190
<font color="#FFFFFF">If I'm being forgotten,
it's because you never</font>

1014
01:04:56,192 --> 01:04:58,061
<font color="#FFFFFF">told anyone
that I wrote them!</font>

1015
01:04:58,063 --> 01:05:01,297
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's crazy! De la Cruz
wrote all his own songs.</font>

1016
01:05:01,298 --> 01:05:03,197
<font color="#FFFFFF">You want to tell him
or should I?</font>

1017
01:05:03,199 --> 01:05:05,599
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hector, I never meant
to take credit.</font>

1018
01:05:05,601 --> 01:05:09,170
<font color="#FFFFFF">We made a great team,
but you died...</font>

1019
01:05:09,172 --> 01:05:11,204
<font color="#FFFFFF">and I only sang your songs</font>

1020
01:05:11,206 --> 01:05:14,208
<font color="#FFFFFF">because I wanted to keep
a part of you alive.</font>

1021
01:05:14,210 --> 01:05:15,943
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, how generous!</font>

1022
01:05:15,945 --> 01:05:18,179
<font color="#FFFFFF">You really did
play together.</font>

1023
01:05:18,181 --> 01:05:20,514
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't want
to fight about it.</font>

1024
01:05:20,516 --> 01:05:22,349
<font color="#FFFFFF">I just want you
to make it right.</font>

1025
01:05:22,353 --> 01:05:26,402
<font color="#FFFFFF">Miguel can put my photo up, and
I can cross over the bridge.</font>

1026
01:05:27,222 --> 01:05:29,123
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can see my girl.</font>

1027
01:05:29,125 --> 01:05:32,094
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ernesto,
remember the night I left?</font>

1028
01:05:32,097 --> 01:05:33,628
<font color="#FFFFFF">That was a long time ago.</font>

1029
01:05:33,632 --> 01:05:35,262
<font color="#FFFFFF">We drank together
and you told me</font>

1030
01:05:35,264 --> 01:05:37,231
<font color="#FFFFFF">you would move
Heaven and Earth...</font>

1031
01:05:37,233 --> 01:05:41,204
<font color="#FFFFFF">for your <i>amigo.</i>
Well, I'm asking you to now.</font>

1032
01:05:41,206 --> 01:05:43,503
<font color="#FFFFFF">Heaven and Earth?
Like in the movie?</font>

1033
01:05:43,505 --> 01:05:46,240
<font color="#FFFFFF">- What?
- That's Don Hidalgo's toast.</font>

1034
01:05:46,242 --> 01:05:48,744
<font color="#FFFFFF">In the de la Cruz movie,
<i>El Camino a Casa.</i></font>

1035
01:05:48,746 --> 01:05:50,144
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm talking about
my real life, Miguel.</font>

1036
01:05:50,146 --> 01:05:52,981
<font color="#FFFFFF">No! It's in there. Look!</font>

1037
01:05:52,983 --> 01:05:54,349
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Never were
truer words spoken.</i></font>

1038
01:05:54,351 --> 01:05:57,518
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>This calls for a toast.
To our friendship!</i></font>

1039
01:05:57,519 --> 01:06:00,222
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I would move Heaven and Earth
for you,</i> mi amigo.</font>

1040
01:06:00,224 --> 01:06:03,358
<font color="#FFFFFF">But in the movie, Don
Hidalgo poisons the drink.</font>

1041
01:06:03,360 --> 01:06:06,309
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Salud!
<i>- Poison!</i></font>

1042
01:06:08,264 --> 01:06:12,768
<font color="#FFFFFF">That night, Ernesto.
The night I left...</font>

1043
01:06:12,771 --> 01:06:15,369
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>We'd been performing
on the road for months.</i></font>

1044
01:06:15,371 --> 01:06:16,672
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I got homesick...</i></font>

1045
01:06:16,675 --> 01:06:18,456
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>and I packed up my songs.</i></font>

1046
01:06:19,009 --> 01:06:20,043
<font color="#FFFFFF">You want to give up now</font>

1047
01:06:20,045 --> 01:06:22,512
<font color="#FFFFFF">when we're this close
to reaching our dream?</font>

1048
01:06:22,514 --> 01:06:24,545
<font color="#FFFFFF">This was your dream.
You'll manage.</font>

1049
01:06:24,547 --> 01:06:26,547
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can't do this
without your songs, Hector.</font>

1050
01:06:26,548 --> 01:06:27,715
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm going home, Ernesto.</font>

1051
01:06:27,717 --> 01:06:30,467
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hate me if you want,
but my mind is made up.</font>

1052
01:06:33,525 --> 01:06:36,793
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, I could never hate you.
If you must go,</font>

1053
01:06:36,795 --> 01:06:39,909
<font color="#FFFFFF">then I'm sending you off
with a toast.</font>

1054
01:06:43,465 --> 01:06:44,733
<font color="#FFFFFF">To our friendship.</font>

1055
01:06:44,735 --> 01:06:49,351
<font color="#FFFFFF">I would move Heaven and Earth
for you, <i>mi amigo. Salud!</i></font>

1056
01:06:53,675 --> 01:06:55,445
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>You walked me
to the train station.</i></font>

1057
01:06:55,447 --> 01:06:58,311
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>But I felt
a pain in my stomach.</i></font>

1058
01:06:58,313 --> 01:07:00,581
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I thought it must have been
something I ate.</i></font>

1059
01:07:00,583 --> 01:07:03,085
<font color="#FFFFFF">Perhaps it was
that <i>chorizo,</i> my friend.</font>

1060
01:07:03,088 --> 01:07:05,635
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Or something I drank.</i></font>

1061
01:07:09,059 --> 01:07:10,907
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I woke up dead.</i></font>

1062
01:07:12,494 --> 01:07:14,762
<font color="#FFFFFF">You poisoned me.</font>

1063
01:07:14,764 --> 01:07:18,300
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're confusing movies
with reality, Hector.</font>

1064
01:07:18,302 --> 01:07:21,951
<font color="#FFFFFF">All this time, I thought
it was just bad luck.</font>

1065
01:07:23,338 --> 01:07:27,057
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>I never thought that
you might have... That you...</i></font>

1066
01:07:30,849 --> 01:07:32,713
<font color="#FFFFFF">- How could you?
- Hector!</font>

1067
01:07:32,715 --> 01:07:34,065
<font color="#FFFFFF">Security! Security!</font>

1068
01:07:34,717 --> 01:07:38,802
<font color="#FFFFFF">You took everything
away from me! You rat!</font>

1069
01:07:39,757 --> 01:07:43,324
<font color="#FFFFFF">Have him taken care of.
He's not well.</font>

1070
01:07:43,327 --> 01:07:48,112
<font color="#FFFFFF">I just wanted to go back home.
No! No!</font>

1071
01:07:49,264 --> 01:07:52,601
<font color="#FFFFFF">I apologize.
Where were we?</font>

1072
01:07:52,603 --> 01:07:54,802
<font color="#FFFFFF">You were going to give me
your blessing.</font>

1073
01:07:54,804 --> 01:07:57,456
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes. Uh, <i>si.</i></font>

1074
01:08:00,376 --> 01:08:04,211
<font color="#FFFFFF">Miguel, uh,
my reputation...</font>

1075
01:08:04,213 --> 01:08:07,682
<font color="#FFFFFF">It is
very important to me.</font>

1076
01:08:07,686 --> 01:08:09,786
<font color="#FFFFFF">I would hate
to have you think...</font>

1077
01:08:09,788 --> 01:08:13,820
<font color="#FFFFFF">That you murdered Hector
for his songs?</font>

1078
01:08:15,260 --> 01:08:18,559
<font color="#FFFFFF">You don't think that.
Do you?</font>

1079
01:08:18,560 --> 01:08:23,546
<font color="#FFFFFF">I... No. Everyone
knows you're the good guy.</font>

1080
01:08:29,771 --> 01:08:32,856
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Papa</i> Ernesto, my blessing?</font>

1081
01:08:34,811 --> 01:08:39,581
<font color="#FFFFFF">Security? Take care of Miguel.
He'll be extending his stay.</font>

1082
01:08:39,582 --> 01:08:42,719
<font color="#FFFFFF">What? But I'm your family!</font>

1083
01:08:42,720 --> 01:08:45,287
<font color="#FFFFFF">And Hector
was my best friend.</font>

1084
01:08:45,289 --> 01:08:48,689
<font color="#FFFFFF">Success doesn't
come for free, Miguel.</font>

1085
01:08:48,690 --> 01:08:50,858
<font color="#FFFFFF">You have to be willing to do
whatever it takes</font>

1086
01:08:50,859 --> 01:08:54,328
<font color="#FFFFFF">to seize your moment.</font>

1087
01:08:54,329 --> 01:08:55,912
<font color="#FFFFFF">I know you understand.</font>

1088
01:08:56,300 --> 01:08:58,847
<font color="#FFFFFF">No! No!</font>

1089
01:09:00,537 --> 01:09:03,471
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let go! No!</font>

1090
01:09:25,895 --> 01:09:30,233
<font color="#FFFFFF">Help!
Can anyone hear me?</font>

1091
01:09:30,234 --> 01:09:32,682
<font color="#FFFFFF">I want to go home.</font>

1092
01:09:51,221 --> 01:09:52,889
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Hector?
- Kid?</font>

1093
01:09:52,890 --> 01:09:55,756
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, Hector!
You were right.</font>

1094
01:09:55,757 --> 01:09:58,359
<font color="#FFFFFF">I should have gone
back to my family.</font>

1095
01:09:58,362 --> 01:10:00,929
<font color="#FFFFFF">They told me not
to be like de la Cruz,</font>

1096
01:10:00,930 --> 01:10:02,764
<font color="#FFFFFF">but I didn't listen.</font>

1097
01:10:02,765 --> 01:10:05,765
<font color="#FFFFFF">I told them I didn't care
if they remembered me.</font>

1098
01:10:05,768 --> 01:10:09,337
<font color="#FFFFFF">I didn't care if I was
on their stupid <i>ofrenda.</i></font>

1099
01:10:09,340 --> 01:10:12,240
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, <i>chamaco.</i>
It's okay. It's okay.</font>

1100
01:10:12,243 --> 01:10:14,859
<font color="#FFFFFF">I told them I didn't care.</font>

1101
01:10:18,548 --> 01:10:21,730
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hector! Hector?</font>

1102
01:10:22,417 --> 01:10:25,654
<font color="#FFFFFF">She's forgetting me.</font>

1103
01:10:25,655 --> 01:10:28,938
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Who?
- My daughter.</font>

1104
01:10:31,362 --> 01:10:35,796
<font color="#FFFFFF">She's the reason you wanted
to cross the bridge.</font>

1105
01:10:35,797 --> 01:10:39,301
<font color="#FFFFFF">I just wanted
to see her again.</font>

1106
01:10:39,302 --> 01:10:41,985
<font color="#FFFFFF">I never should have
left Santa Cecilia.</font>

1107
01:10:43,039 --> 01:10:45,039
<font color="#FFFFFF">I wish I could apologize.</font>

1108
01:10:45,042 --> 01:10:49,043
<font color="#FFFFFF">I wish I could tell her that her
<i>papa</i> was trying to come home.</font>

1109
01:10:49,046 --> 01:10:51,630
<font color="#FFFFFF">That he loved her so much.</font>

1110
01:10:53,951 --> 01:10:55,864
<font color="#FFFFFF">My Coco...</font>

